2026-05-14T19:35:32.6780476Z 18        system downgrades it to a heads-up notification, which is fine —
2026-05-14T19:35:32.6781140Z 19        we only request it when the toggle is on.
2026-05-14T19:35:32.6781645Z 20    -->
2026-05-14T19:35:32.6782214Z 21    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.USE_FULL_SCREEN_INTENT" />
